| Aggregation  | Structural | Weak (shared)       | Hollow diamond  | `Team` â€“ `Player`       |
| Composition  | Structural | Strong (owns)       | Filled diamond  | `House` â€“ `Room`        |
| Inheritance  | Structural | "is-a" hierarchy    | Hollow triangle | `Dog` â€“ `Animal`        |
| Dependency   | Behavioral | Temporary use       | Dashed arrow    | `CarService` â€“ `Engine` |



